properties.text:
When the water is too warm, corals expel the algae in their tissue, causing coral bleaching. Global warming and pollution are leading causes of this phenomenon. Unfortunately, bleached corals are more likely to die.

[color=#57ce34]Objective:[/color] Save [color=#a3a3ff]13 corals[/color] by using your [color=#a3a3ff]magical seeds[/color] on them to cool the water and clear surrounding pollution.

[color=#57ce34]How to play:[/color] [color=#a3a3ff]\[ARROWS][/color] to swim and [color=#a3a3ff]\[SPACE][/color] to spread seeds. Refill your oxygen in breathable areas.
                                                      Press [color=#57ce34]\[SPACE][/color] to begin...
